Usage: ./pokemon_analysis.sh <file_name> [options]
Options:
  -h, --help          Display this help message.
  -i, --info          Display the highest adjusted and raw usage.
  -s, --sort <col>    Sort the data by the specified column.
    name              Sort by Pokemon name.
    usage             Sort by Adjusted Usage.
    raw               Sort by Raw Usage.
    hp                Sort by HP.
    atk               Sort by Attack.
    def               Sort by Defense.
    spatk             Sort by Special Attack.
    spdef             Sort by Special Defense.
    speed             Sort by Speed.
  -g, --grep <name>   Search for a specific Pokémon sorted by usage.
  -f, --filter <type> Filter by type of Pokémon sorted by usage.
